          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Honor and Remember Flag Recognition Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill designates the Honor and Remember Flag, created by Honor and Remember, Inc., as a national symbol to honor service members who died in the line of duty and specifies federal locations and dates for its display.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
